@HostAddress = http://localhost:5127

### 1. 測試發送 Teams 通知 (使用 Teams-Web Detector Key)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/notifications/teams
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: a1b2c3d4-report-secret-key-e5f6g7h8

{
  "targetChannel": "default",
  "title": "測試通知",
  "message": "這是一條來自 .http 檔案的測試訊息 (User: Teams-Web Detector)"
}

### 2. 測試發送 Teams 通知 (使用 Client Other Key)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/notifications/teams
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: Client Other Key

{
  "targetChannel": "default",
  "title": "測試通知",
  "message": "這是一條來自 .http 檔案的測試訊息 (User: Client Other Key)"
}

### 3. 測試無效的 API Key (應回傳 401)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/notifications/teams
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: invalid-key

{
  "targetChannel": "default",
  "title": "測試失敗",
  "message": "這條訊息不應該被發送"
}
